channel.title: Element-Pkz [Delta]
channel.description:
This isn't my name, in-fact I'm not hosting the server. I was appointed as the head developer though, so i cannot choose the name. Please Lay off.
Source: Pbscape Client: Pbscape
Why- I am completely rewriting the server. I chose this source because, of the client. I like the 600+ interface, and I'm to lazy to add it.
Skills: I'm only listing the ones, I have written.
Herblore: 50% rewritten, inputted into it's own class. Woodcutting: 100% rewritten, inputted into it's own class.
Custom Classes: Godsword: 100% rewritten, cleaned out of the source.java, and into it's own class. SpiritShield: 100% rewritten, cleaned out of the client.java, and into it's own class. StaffofLight: 100% rewritten, cleaned out of the client.java, and into it's own class.
To-Do: Finish Rewriting Skills. Finish Rewriting Minigames. Finish adding Models. Just the lava, and lime whip models. I cannot find any of them. Finish cleaning the client.java.
Other Achievements: Changed Home to Edgeville. Changed original home to a shops teleport.
Original client.java file: 960kb
Current client.java file: 889kb
Media: [IMG]http://i1182.photobucket.com/albums/x453/Ampzor2011/Progress.png[/img]
More Later!
Support:
Thanks to: Pblord7- Client/Source RandQm- Packaging the server/ helping with some files Imsuperman05- I don't exactly know, but i'm sure he has helped in some way lol. Mopar Tuts.
Current Client.java Cleaning Total: 71kbs
